n, every family apart; the family of the house of David apart, and their wives apart; the family of the house of Nathan apart, and their wives apart;", "The family of the house of Levi apart, and their wives apart; the family of Shimei apart, and their wives apart;", "All the families that remain, every family apart, and their wives apart."], "book_name": "Section", "summary": "In the final great war, all nations shall be engaged at Jerusalem but the Lord shall defend his people\u2014Then the Jews shall look upon Jesus whom they crucified, and there shall be great mourning."}